{"tid":1054381,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好矛盾呀我","createTime":"2019-03-09T18:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T19:27:54.000Z","uid":145685,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7d0dd3d8f94daffb3e6fc111bf2f5947c0dca1b7","tid":1054381,"uid":145685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:46:33.000Z","msg":"有一個男仔<br />\n一開波識覺得佢好可愛 係我鐘意個啲類型<br />\n之後有繼續聯絡 見下面食下飯咁<br />\n都啱傾又幾開心咁<br />\n<br />\n但係我啲心情好撚飄忽<br />\n一時覺得同佢一齊好正好開心<br />\n聽到佢把聲同見到佢張相都會忍唔住含春笑 <br />\n覺得佢好得意好掛住佢<br />\n<br />\n一時又覺得同佢未必係想像中咁好<br />\n又想逃避 唔想同佢繼續咁落去<br />\n我自己都唔知點解<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔肯定自己想點 唔知係想同佢一齊定純粹想做下朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得我真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46068d0082929b5855aba2f7ea6b79b48e3825a","tid":1054381,"uid":208270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:48:10.000Z","msg":"差唔多情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我簡直係矛盾嘅存在"},{"pid":"de66515a626311004e5c2b27c3d4fa033de11bbc","tid":1054381,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:49:52.000Z","msg":"好想有個女仔會咁諗我"},{"pid":"6df43d3105b79faf5bb2c4106afb2415217ea4ab","tid":1054381,"uid":145685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d46068d0082929b5855aba2f7ea6b79b48e3825a","tid":1054381,"uid":208270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:48:10.000Z","msg":"差唔多情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我簡直係矛盾嘅存在"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:50:28.000Z","msg":"好辛苦 搞到啲fd想幫我 問下我想點<br />\n好似淨係識答 我唔知呀。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d71434c17baa18bd553b7d6a9b99fd608771d2","tid":1054381,"uid":145685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de66515a626311004